          "thinking": "Now I have a very clear picture. Let me check the policy document on travel_lodging to see what the standard limit is for this expense type. But first, let me check what the authorization management policy says.\n\nThe key anomalies I've found:\n\n1. **Split reimbursement (拆分报销)**: \n   - Employee E0007 (李丽娟) submitted two travel_lodging reimbursements of 5200 each (R004207 on Jan 10 and R004208 on Jan 12)\n   - Same employee, same expense type within 7 days (only 2 days apart)\n   - Both with reason \"拆分报销注入样本1\" \n   - Combined total: 10400\n   - Violates Article 11 of 01_expense_reimbursement_2025.md\n\nNow I need to determine what anomaly IDs to assign. Let me look at the policy further to understand what specific anomalies are defined.\n\nActually, let me check the authorization management policy for the approval limits.",
